title: Armani Code By Giorgio Armani For Women. Eau De Parfume Spray 1.7 oz
description: Launched by the design house of Giorgio Armani.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: SHANY Professional Eyeshadow Pallette, Runway Collection, 162 Colors
